text.tspan: Step 1: Thread the inner cable through the handle.
Step 2: Thread the outer cable (1) with the cable hat onto the inner cable.
Step 3: Thread the power_modulator to the inner cable with the large hole of the

step 4: Thread the inner cable through the splitter, and secure the cable clamp -
- nipple to the inner cable into the splitter, with the slide block in the longest
Step 5: Install the cables (3) & (4), and bundling the inner cables.
